    "message": "feat(github): phase 1 step 0 — capture mode, HMAC webhooks, poller skeleton\n\n- config: sources.github (api_token, webhook_secret, poll_interval, repos,\n  infra_path), Duration YAML type, capture_dir returns with its reader,\n  WTC_GH_* env overrides\n- store: migration 0002 github_poll_state + monotonic watermark accessors\n- server: POST /ingest/github with X-Hub-Signature-256 verification\n  (constant-time, body-bound, fail-closed when unconfigured); capture mode\n  dumps raw bodies+headers per source for fixture freezing\n- ingest/github: hand-rolled REST client (runs/prs/commits — no SDK dep)\n  and poller loop with bounded 24h first-run backfill; normalization lands\n  in step 2 once real fixtures are frozen (fixture-first rule)\n- serve: --capture-dir flag, poller wired behind token+repos+interval config\n\nNormalizers intentionally absent: no parser without golden fixtures.",
